      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/171/5731",
      "text": [
        " كَانَ أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَقُولُ : فِي اَلرَّجُلِ اَلْحُرِّ يَمُوتُ وَ لَهُ أُمٌّ مَمْلُوكَةٌ قَالَ \"تُشْتَرَى مِنْ مَالِ اِبْنِهَا ثُمَّ تُعْتَقُ ثُمَّ يُوَرَّثُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5731 - Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said that Commander of the Faithful (as) used to say regarding a free man who dies while his mother is a slave:\n\"She should be purchased from the wealth of her son, then freed, and then she will inherit from him.\""
        ]
      }
    },
